page.title: 19House sale in Glenrothes
page.content: 5 Fingask Avenue, Pitteuchar, Glenrothes. Detached luxury executive bungalow situated in small development in prime residential area.The houuse has been finished to a high standard. Accommodation comprises_entrance hall, lounge,dining room,master bedroom with ensuite shower room,three bedrooms,exceptionally well fitted kitchen,utility room and bathroom.Full gas central heating and double glazing throughout.Double garage fitted with power,water and workbench.Attractive features.Original stone built fireplace.Large paved patio.Garden to front and rear.Immediate entry.Viewing by appointment only.
